data.description: Charming 1946 home with tons of character. Hardwood floors, arched doorways, and formal dining room.  Cozy nook to enjoy your morning coffee.  Kitchen has granite countertops, cork floors, and pantry.  Large master bedroom with walk-in closet, plus two other closets.  Family/game room downstairs. Could be a 3rd bedroom.  Extra room downstairs that if finished can be a 4th bedroom.  Huge .32 lot with underground sprinklers and landscaped. Oversized single car garage.  RV/extra parking. All appliances stay.
